'''和風醬'''（{{lang-ja|和風ドレッシング}}）或'''和風沙拉醬'''，是一種以[[土佐酢|土佐酢]]為基底的[[沙拉醬|沙拉醬]]，風行於日本和台灣<ref>{{cite book   | title = Authentic Recipes from Japan | author= Takayuki Kosaki & Walter Wagner |publisher = Tuttle Publishing | location=   |url = https://books.google.com/?id=TjfRAgAAQBAJ&pg=PT70&dq=tosazu#v=onepage&q=tosazu&f=false | date = 2013  | page =  | isbn = 9781462905720 | accessdate = 29 February 2016 }}</ref>。

和風醬成份複雜，呈現略微的酸味和鹹味，一般由日式醬油、米醋、味醂與植物油調製而成。亦有許多種類，例如加入[[青海苔|青海苔]]、[[紫蘇|紫蘇]]、薑末、鰹節、梅醬、山葵、檸檬或柚子。<ref>{{cite book   | title = The Japanese Grill: From Classic Yakitori to Steak, Seafood, and Vegetables | author= Tadashi Ono & Harris Salat |publisher = Potter/TenSpeed/Harmony | location=   |url = https://books.google.com/?id=ODAe_boHajsC&pg=PA183&dq=wafu+dressing#v=onepage&q=wafu%20dressing&f=false | date = 2011  | pages =  163 | isbn = 9781607740667 | accessdate = 29 February 2016 }}</ref>

